snippet.title: [Nvidia Shield] The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess Trailer
snippet.description:
*Note: This YouTube channel is not sponsored by or affiliated with Nintendo or Nvidia.

The official trailer for The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess on Nvidia Shield consoles in Mainland China.
The trailer is in 720P, but original game has been upscaled to 1080P.
Official website: https://shield.nvidia.cn/games/geforce-now/legend-of-zelda-princess-at-dusk

This video is an unofficial reupload.
Source: https://weibo.com/6154885380/FzNd389uX
